<br>
Mage has to be one of the best combo's for a monk. Why?  Bandaids, Weight Reduction Bags, Food, Water, Throwing daggers etc.  We almost never have to hit town heh  I don't think even a Cleric/Warrior could beat this combo.<br>
<br>
If you are going for a Caster/Caster combo I'd have to agree with the Necro/Mage idea <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START :) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/smile.gif ALT=":)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END--> <br>
